                <li><strong>Supported Formats:</strong> PDF to Word, Excel, and PowerPoint only.</li>
                <li><strong>Basic Tools:</strong> Basic tools for merging and splitting PDFs.</li>
                <li><strong>Basic Security:</strong> Basic encryption of files during transfer.</li>
                <li><strong>Community Support:</strong> Access to a community support forum.</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="">Choose</a>
        </div>
        <div>
            <h2>$7/month</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Advanced Conversion:</strong> Convert to and from a wide range of formats, including PDF to image, ePub, HTML, etc.</li>
                <li><strong>Higher File Size Limit:</strong> Convert PDF files up to 100 MB.</li>
                <li><strong>Unlimited Conversions:</strong> Unlimited conversions per month.</li>
                <li><strong>No Watermark:</strong> Converted files do not contain a watermark.</li>
                <li><strong>Ad-Free:</strong> Use the application without any ads.</li>
                <li><strong>Advanced Tools:</strong> Advanced tools for PDF editing, text recognition (OCR), and PDF compression.</li>
                <li><strong>Advanced Security:</strong> End-to-end encryption of files and password protection for PDFs.</li>
                <li><strong>Priority Support:</strong> Access to priority customer support via email and live chat.</li>
                <li><strong>Cloud Storage:</strong> Integrated cloud storage to save and access converted PDF files.</li>
                <li><strong>Conversion History:</strong> Access to complete conversion history for easy document management.</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="">Choose</a>
        </div>
    </section>
{% endblock %}
